f'        prevents \u003cbase href\u003e from rewriting all\n                         relative URLs to an attacker-controlled origin\n- form-action 'self'     prevents form submissions to off-origin URLs\n                         (incl. via the formaction button attribute);\n                         also a partial CSRF defense layer\n- object-src 'none'      kills the legacy plugin attack surface\n                         (\u003cobject\u003e, \u003cembed\u003e, \u003capplet\u003e — Flash, Java\n                         applet, PDF plugins) which DHIS2 doesn't use\n\nFactor as a private COMMON_HARDENING constant in CspConstants so all\nfour emitted policies (default, user-uploaded, app-host, openapi-docs)\ninherit the hardening uniformly. Add a regression-guard unit test that\nfails if any of the three is dropped from any emitted policy.\n\nThese are listed by name in the original CSP_REPORT.md §3.1.\n\nAI Assisted","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"51436caae59414770bb02ddd7dfd3a0e139b15d4","tree_id":"2839b956d8a01886258795bf3e0fb8bc6ad2210f","timestamp":"2026-05-01T16:36:23Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url"